## Working style

- **Micro-implementation is test-driven** (red-green-refactor). See `general/tdd.md`.
- **Design is DDD**: ubiquitous language, layering, pure domain. See `general/ddd.md`.
{% if 'python' in languages %}- **Python runs through `uv`** — never `python`, `pip`, `poetry` directly.
{% endif %}- See `{{ ai_folder }}/skills/` and `{{ ai_folder }}/agents/` for invokable
  skills and subagents.

## Source layout

```
src/application/      Use cases, services, orchestration
src/domain/           Pure business logic (entities, value objects, interfaces)
src/infrastructure/   DB, network, drivers, external adapters
src/presentation/     Entry points (HTTP routers, CLI, ISRs)
tests/{unit,integration,e2e,performance}
```

Empty directories are prefixed with `_` until they receive their first file.

